    <p align="justify">The <strong>First Ground Station workshop</strong>,  conducted on 12th October, 2008 at IITB, which was to enable students  to learn the technology of making a ground station. We hope that  through these workshops, student teams will be able to make a working  low cost ground station (&lt;20,000 Rs) capable of receiving signals  and data from our satellite. Around 8 universities participated in this  workshop.</p>
